## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="31284-104">默认情况下, WMI 方法的名称将是目标方法的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-104">By default, the WMI method name will be the name of the target method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="31284-105">此属性<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementMemberAttribute>的父类包含一个名称参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-105">The parent class of this attribute, <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementMemberAttribute>, includes a Name parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="31284-106">您可以使用该参数更改通过 WMI 公开的方法的名称, 而无需更改您的内部方法名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-106">You can use that parameter to change the name of the method that is exposed through WMI without changing your internal method name.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="31284-107">方法必须是公共的, 并且它可能是静态的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-107">The method must be public and it may be static.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="31284-108">它可以包含 [in]、[out]、[in/out]、数组或对象引用参数的任意组合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-108">It can include any combination of [in], [out], [in/out], array or object reference parameters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="31284-109">由于 WMI 施加的限制, 数组参数不能是多维或交错的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-109">Array parameters cannot be multidimensional or jagged because of limitations imposed by WMI.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="31284-110">方法的返回类型可以是 void、标量、string、datetime 或 object。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-110">The return type of the method can be: void, scalar, string, datetime or object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="31284-111">它不能是数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-111">It cannot be an array.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="31284-112">下面的示例演示如何使用 ManagementTask 特性标记方法以便向 WMI 公开方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-112">The following example shows how to mark a method with the ManagementTask attribute to expose the method to WMI.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="31284-113">此方法将在 WMI 中显示为 ResetCounters。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="31284-113">The method will show up in WMI as ResetCounters.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementTask attribute to specify that a method  
// is exposed to WMI through this provider. Consumers will be  
// able to execute this method through WMI.  
[ManagementTask]  
public void ResetCounters()  
{  
    counter.Reset();  
}  
```
